queryData.query:
SELECT gender AS gender,
       state AS state,
       name AS name,
       DATE_TRUNC('year', ds) AS __timestamp,
       sum(num) AS total,
       sum(sum_boys) AS boys,
       sum(CASE
               WHEN state = 'CA' THEN num
               ELSE 0
           END) AS "SUM(num_california)",
       SUM(sum_boys)/SUM(num) AS pct_boys,
       sum(num) AS "SUM(num)"
FROM birth_names
WHERE ds >= '1920-06-06 00:00:00.000000'
  AND ds < '2020-06-06 13:06:05.000000'
GROUP BY gender,
         state,
         name,
         DATE_TRUNC('year', ds)
ORDER BY "SUM(num)" DESC
LIMIT 2000
